<p>Any ideas why this is not producing a smooth circle?</p>  <pre><code>public void draw(ShapeRenderer sRenderer) {      sRenderer.begin(ShapeType.Filled);     sRenderer.setColor(1.0f, 0.0f, 0.0f, 0.0f);     sRenderer.identity();     sRenderer.translate(1.0f, 1.0f, 0);     sRenderer.rotate(0.0f, 0.0f, 1.0f, (float) Math.toDegrees(getBody().getAngle()));     sRenderer.circle(0.0f, 0.0f, 1.0f);     sRenderer.end(); } </code></pre>  <p><a href="http://i.stack.imgur.com/tN8wO.png" rel="nofollow"><img src="http://i.stack.imgur.com/tN8wO.png" alt="screenshot"></a></p>